<p>Better yet, get your character with another character, fast. Get them together and get the action started. Let their actions and words show their thoughts. Youâ€”stay out of their heads.</p>

<p>And while youâ€™re avoiding â€œthoughtâ€ verbs, be very wary about using the bland verbs â€œisâ€ and â€œhave.â€ For example:</p>

