<p>Please. For now, hate me all you want, but donâ€™t use thought verbs. After Christmas, go crazy, but Iâ€™d bet money you wonâ€™t.</p>

<p>For this monthâ€™s homework, pick through your writing and circle every â€œthoughtâ€ verb. Then, find some way to eliminate it. Kill it by un-packing it.</p>

